OL,5, Amazon workers are staging the first   
OL,6, ever UK strike on Wednesday against the
OL,7, online giant in a protest over pay.    
OL,9,FAround 300 staff walked out at Amazon's
OL,10,FCoventry warehouse, the GMB union said,
OL,11,Fover what they called a "derisory" 5%  
OL,12,Fpay rise to #10.50 an hour.            
OL,14,FWorkers told the BBC about "severe"    
OL,15,Fconditions, claiming they are          
OL,16,Fconstantly monitored and upbraided for 
OL,17,F"idle time" lasting just a few minutes.
OL,19,FAmazon said it has a system "that      
OL,20,Frecognises great performance".         
